{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0991b81ccf","title":"致新三害分子","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"464bef25be","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0991b81ccf"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"765ec99bb5","name":"龙英华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f6921d7747","type":"title","text":"致新三害分子","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"309ac8027c","type":"authors","text":"北京大学龙英华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"3997e26746","type":"paragraph","text":"陈谷风、施光享、唐天然诸同学，你们写了“修正主义者宣言”“清除龙英华建议”等等，你们的目的是打击正直的共产党员，你们的理由是杜勒斯式的捏造，历史将判决你们是整风运动中的新三害分子。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"38aa609e3e","type":"paragraph","text":" （哲一  龙英华启）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"f36cac9ee0","type":"subtitle","text":"因故辞职","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"15df8b2c06","type":"paragraph","text":"一、本人目前忙于准备考试和参加辩论会无时间参加“广场”工作，特辞去编委职。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"2ca9661d6c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“广场”的事业是正义的，目前的运动是波浪式的起伏前进的。我建议“广场”第一期改出小型油印版、整顿稿件、提高质量。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"f0ba3e4a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“广场”工作有缺点的一面，而（是）次要的，可逐步改进。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"2edecbac83","type":"paragraph","text":"四、“广场”支持者们与反对者们的矛盾是人民内部矛盾，是社会主义社会内部诸阶层矛盾的反映。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"515dfca60d","type":"paragraph","text":"五、“广场”还缺少足够的人才，“广场”应开贤路招贤进士。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"bbb66a1dfc","type":"paragraph","text":"六、建议“广场”成为小资产阶级的刊物，多登一些反映小资产阶级要求的讨论、政论。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"0410a4cc3d","type":"paragraph","text":"七、“广场”要改造自己并冲破黎明前的黑暗。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"87be45eec3","type":"paragraph","text":"哲一  龙英华","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"},{"id":"0b6e6d77a9","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf"}],"page":{"id":"36ff811ac0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0991b81ccf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}